{"tid":1097835,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲人自製簡體字路標","createTime":"2019-04-08T15:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T17:07:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6a2197b5571a54841833d8eddb13434ef1c08b","tid":1097835,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190408/20650972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F20650972&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfpzUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=41874635\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F20650972&h=0c4ea4ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190408/20650972</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳洲人自製簡體字路標 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190408/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190408%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=d3a1607f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.3aw.com.au\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.3aw.com.au&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfpzUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=8a02bd34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.3aw.com.au</a>圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n自從手持香港發出的國際車牌的中國勞工在澳洲大洋路駕駛，無視Stop Sign，以時速100公里的車速攔腰直撞橫線車輛，令澳洲司機枉死之後，當地人人心惶惶，對中國司機的駕駛能力及駕駛態度聞風喪膽，大洋路居民紛紛自製中文簡體字路標，掛在英文Stop Sign下面：「停車！停車！停車！必須停車3秒！必須左看右看！」<br />\n<br />\n不過，根據維多利亞省的《道路安全條例》，任何人私自設立路標均屬違法行為，當局要求居民移走自設的路標。記者訪問了不少當地人，他們對這些自設路標的反應卻都相當正面，認為有助於看不懂英文路標的中國人理解道路使用規則，從而令他們安心。<br />\n<br />\n說穿了，只不過是消極應對。中國是不能頒發國際車牌的，也就是說，假如有中國人去外國旅遊而手持國際車牌，只有兩個可能性，一是手持假的國際車牌；二是他們的國際車牌從香港獲得。香港運輸署若不正視問題，則最終結果是令香港運輸署發出的車牌失去公信力。<br />\n<br />\n如果運輸署不曾審核中國駕照持有人的駕駛能力及道路使用知識，而胡亂發出國際車牌，這些香港發出的國際車牌持有人在其他國家製造的交通意外數字一旦增加，到最後，民眾的消極應對必然會促成政府的積極面對。受影響的，終究會是外遊租車的香港人。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n幸好不用考中學文憑試 (古德明)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n大聲公 (楊靜)"},{"pid":"badd956e5c02822361114a2c2435d9493e94407b","tid":1097835,"uid":69603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:35:13.000Z","msg":"天朝大國 雄起了 <br />\n全世界都有殘体字"},{"pid":"62ceca8dfe5ee406569f648223759db0e5d84085","tid":1097835,"uid":28331,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"外國鬼仔都跪拜咱強国跨下"},{"pid":"41b79eedb55e94b1adfd0a74b482358a8330e21c","tid":1097835,"uid":219284,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"棟完塊牌個感覺即刻變撚左大陸咁"},{"pid":"a52d6a434d68bec5e74b38d3d850f3e5136eb85c","tid":1097835,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T20:38:01.000Z","msg":"咁細隻字鬼睇到"},{"pid":"ecfaa4f6336346a793e82877354e3b8ae8b43f50","tid":1097835,"uid":8410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T20:48:00.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩！ 佢地以為中國人會守規則？"},{"pid":"b05923622b540aeeccb4817b4213f92876c48b48","tid":1097835,"uid":75072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:02:45.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的國 澳洲人都寫中文了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b891697d133304b664b237a53e0f0b26c0ca1a9","tid":1097835,"uid":208952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"其實香港人揸車都唔好得去邊<br />\n十個九個都停線當讓線"},{"pid":"02ddd19f6d6e372de6578e696ee074f25e939797","tid":1097835,"uid":2346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b891697d133304b664b237a53e0f0b26c0ca1a9","tid":1097835,"uid":208952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"其實香港人揸車都唔好得去邊<br />\n十個九個都停線當讓線"},